items.name: case unknown
items.desc: Error code indicating that an unknown or unexpected error occurred.

items.name: case clientInvalid
items.desc: Error code indicating that the client is not allowed to perform the attempted action.

items.name: case paymentCancelled
items.desc: Error code indicating that the user canceled a payment request.

items.name: case paymentInvalid
items.desc: Error code indicating that one of the payment parameters wasn’t recognized by the App Store.

items.name: case paymentNotAllowed
items.desc: Error code indicating that the user is not allowed to authorize payments.

items.name: case storeProductNotAvailable
items.desc: Error code indicating that the requested product is not available in the store.

items.name: case cloudServicePermissionDenied
items.desc: Error code indicating that the user has not allowed access to Cloud service information.

items.name: case cloudServiceNetworkConnectionFailed
items.desc: Error code indicating that the device could not connect to the network.

items.name: case cloudServiceRevoked
items.desc: Error code indicating that the user has revoked permission to use this cloud service.

items.name: case privacyAcknowledgementRequired
items.desc: Error code indicating that the user has not yet acknowledged Apple’s privacy policy for Apple Music.

items.name: case unauthorizedRequestData
items.desc: Error code indicating that the app is attempting to use a property for which it does not have the required entitlement.

items.name: case invalidOfferIdentifier
items.desc: Error code indicating that the offer identifier is invalid.

items.name: case invalidOfferPrice
items.desc: Error code indicating that the price you specified in App Store Connect is no longer valid.

items.name: case invalidSignature
items.desc: Error code indicating that the signature in a payment discount isn’t valid.

items.name: case missingOfferParams
items.desc: Error code indicating that parameters are missing in a payment discount.

items.name: case ineligibleForOffer
items.desc: An error code that indicates the user is ineligible for the subscription offer.

items.name: case overlayCancelled
items.desc: An error code that indicates the cancellation of an overlay.

items.name: case overlayInvalidConfiguration
items.desc: An error code that indicates the overlay’s configuration is invalid.

items.name: case unsupportedPlatform
items.desc: An error code that indicates the current platform doesn’t support overlays.
